            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJob%201%3A1-3%3A26%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJob%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EPrologue%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20once%20was%20a%20man%20named%20Job%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Uz.%20He%20was%20blameless%26%23x2014%3Ba%20man%20of%20complete%20integrity.%20He%20feared%20God%20and%20stayed%20away%20from%20evil.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20had%20seven%20sons%20and%20three%20daughters.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20owned%207%2C000%20sheep%2C%203%2C000%20camels%2C%20500%26%23xA0%3Bteams%20of%20oxen%2C%20and%20500%26%23xA0%3Bfemale%20donkeys.%20He%20also%20had%20many%20servants.%20He%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20richest%20person%20in%20that%20entire%20area.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EJob%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sons%20would%20take%20turns%20preparing%20feasts%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20they%20would%20also%20invite%20their%20three%20sisters%20to%20celebrate%20with%20them.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20these%20celebrations%20ended%26%23x2014%3Bsometimes%20after%20several%20days%26%23x2014%3BJob%20would%20purify%20his%20children.%20He%20would%20get%20up%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20offer%20a%20burnt%20offering%20for%20each%20of%20them.%20For%20Job%20said%20to%20himself%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPerhaps%20my%20children%20have%20sinned%20and%20have%20cursed%20God%20in%20their%20hearts.%26%23x201D%3B%20This%20was%20Job%26%23x2019%3Bs%20regular%20practice.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJob%26%23x2019%3Bs%20First%20Test%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20the%20members%20of%20the%20heavenly%20court%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A6a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20sons%20of%20God.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20came%20to%20present%20themselves%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20Accuser%2C%20Satan%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A6b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eand%20the%20satan%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20similarly%20throughout%20this%20chapter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20came%20with%20them.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhere%20have%20you%20come%20from%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20asked%20Satan.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3ESatan%20answered%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20been%20patrolling%20the%20earth%2C%20watching%20everything%20that%26%23x2019%3Bs%20going%20on.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20asked%20Satan%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHave%20you%20noticed%20my%20servant%20Job%3F%20He%20is%20the%20finest%20man%20in%20all%20the%20earth.%20He%20is%20blameless%26%23x2014%3Ba%20man%20of%20complete%20integrity.%20He%20fears%20God%20and%20stays%20away%20from%20evil.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESatan%20replied%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYes%2C%20but%20Job%20has%20good%20reason%20to%20fear%20God.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20have%20always%20put%20a%20wall%20of%20protection%20around%20him%20and%20his%20home%20and%20his%20property.%20You%20have%20made%20him%20prosper%20in%20everything%20he%20does.%20Look%20how%20rich%20he%20is!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_11%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20reach%20out%20and%20take%20away%20everything%20he%20has%2C%20and%20he%20will%20surely%20curse%20you%20to%20your%20face!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_12%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAll%20right%2C%20you%20may%20test%20him%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Satan.%20%26%23x201C%3BDo%20whatever%20you%20want%20with%20everything%20he%20possesses%2C%20but%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20harm%20him%20physically.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20Satan%20left%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_13%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20when%20Job%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sons%20and%20daughters%20were%20feasting%20at%20the%20oldest%20brother%26%23x2019%3Bs%20house%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_14%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3Ea%20messenger%20arrived%20at%20Job%26%23x2019%3Bs%20home%20with%20this%20news%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BYour%20oxen%20were%20plowing%2C%20with%20the%20donkeys%20feeding%20beside%20them%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_15%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3Ewhen%20the%20Sabeans%20raided%20us.%20They%20stole%20all%20the%20animals%20and%20killed%20all%20the%20farmhands.%20I%20am%20the%20only%20one%20who%20escaped%20to%20tell%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_16%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EWhile%20he%20was%20still%20speaking%2C%20another%20messenger%20arrived%20with%20this%20news%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BThe%20fire%20of%20God%20has%20fallen%20from%20heaven%20and%20burned%20up%20your%20sheep%20and%20all%20the%20shepherds.%20I%20am%20the%20only%20one%20who%20escaped%20to%20tell%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_1_17%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EWhile%20he%20was%20still%20speaking%2C%20a%20third%20messenger%20arrived%20with%20this%20news%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BThree%20bands%20of%20Chaldean%20raiders%20have%20stolen%20your%20camels%20and%20killed%20your%20servants.%20I